Package: stools
Title: Tools for survey data handling
Version: 0.7.1
Authors@R: person("Jouni", "Vatanen", email = "jounipvatanen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Miscellaneous functions for survey data handling. API functions for Surveypal survey tool, wrappers for DBI::dbWriteTable, data cleaning, brand colors and plots.
